ce libraries and best practices;&bull;    You actively write unit tests for new code;&bull;    You write highly performant code and know how to performance tune Android apps;&bull;    Youre self-driven to improve the app and codebase above and beyond whats outlined in the spec;&bull;    You have experience building, maintaining, or otherwise contributing to open source projects;&bull;    You are familiar with MVP , Kotlin, RxJava and other libraries in our tech stack;&bull;    Understand Android SDK;&bull;    Know android dynamic-component-framework and dynamic-plugin-framework.', '2018-04-13 11:20:15', '2018-04-13 17:36:20', null);
